{
  "id": "adv_group_sun_04_05",
  "title": "サニーピース 04 05",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "――ということがあって、その日から私は\nサニピに入れてもらえるようにアピールを始めたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――that's what happened‚ and from that day‚\nI started making an appeal to be allowed into Sunny Peace",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "え？　そんなアピールをしていたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Did you make that appeal?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.8733332952,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "はあ……やっぱり気付いていなかったのね\n結構あからさまにアピールしていたつもりなんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… I guess you didn't notice\nI thought I was making a pretty obvious appeal",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.9333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5766.666666699999,
          "startTime": 21.7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-00-000-noon",
      "startTime": 21.0463041942
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君、お仕事お疲れ様\nお茶を入れたから少し休憩しましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-kun‚ nice work\nI've made some tea‚ so let's take a short break",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.5333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cup-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4633.333333299997,
          "startTime": 27.7333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\n……いい香りですね。もしかして、茶葉を変えました？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you\n…It smells good. Did you change the tea leaves?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、ちょっと奮発していいお茶にしてみたの\nところで、新ユニットのメンバーは決まったのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I splurged a little and got some high-quality tea\nBy the way‚ have the members of the new unit been decided?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、まだ悩んでいる最中です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I'm still thinking about it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.4907521566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "そう……私で力になれることならなんでも言ってね！\n本当に遠慮なんてしなくていいから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So… if there's anything I can do to help‚ please let me know!\nYou really don't have to be shy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\nじゃあ、このデータの入力をお願いしてもいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you\nThen‚ can I ask you to enter this data?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "え？　え、ええ、もちろんいいわよ\n遙子さんに任せなさい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? S-Sure‚ of course\nLeave it to Haruko-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――30分後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――30 minutes later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.7886153063,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6444.7180269999935,
          "startTime": 80.2333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "お茶が入ったわよ。少し休憩に……あぁっ！\nいっけなーい、持っていた写真を落としちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've made some tea. Let's take a… oops!\nOh noー‚ I dropped the photo I had",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "拾うの手伝いますよ\n……この写真、遙子さんが自分で撮ったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll help you pick it up\n…Did you take this photo yourself‚ Haruko-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.2333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 86.8299082916
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "そうよ、明るい日差しの下で撮ってみたんだけど\nこうして見ると私って太陽が似合うと思わない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I took it in bright sunlight\nLooking at it this way‚ don't you think the sun suits me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　そういえば太陽のように輝くアイドルグループを\n作りたいって言ってたわね。なんだか奇遇ね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! You said you wanted to create an idol group\nthat shines like the sun. What a coincidence~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "この写真……\n逆光になってて顔が見えないんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This photo……\nIt's backlit‚ so I can't see your face……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それに、急に写真だなんてどうしたんですか？\nあ……遙子さん、もしかして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And why did you suddenly have to take a photo?\nAh…… Haruko-san‚ perhaps…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "今の宣材写真を撮り直したいんですか！？\n気が付かなくてすみません！　検討しておきます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you want to change your current profile photo!?\nI'm sorry I didn't notice! I'll consider it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.3666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "あ、うん……そうね、よろしく……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ yeah… That's right‚ thanks…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.183599965,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――さらに30分後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Another 30 minutes later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.2367509527,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "お茶が入ったわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've made some tea",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.2700875921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　遙子さん、さっきまで私服でしたよね？\nどうして制服に着替えたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Haruko-san‚ you were in casual clothes just a moment ago?\nWhy did you change into your school uniform?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "もっと若さをアピールしようかな～と思って……\nほら、「若さが眩しい」ってよく言うでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was thinking I'd try to look more youthful…\nI thought I would try to appeal to a younger feel~…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.4333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "私は眩しい存在になりたいの、そう……太陽みたいに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey look‚ you often hear‚ 'Youth is dazzling'‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.4799522084,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "新しいキャッチフレーズも考えたから聞いてくれる？\n「佐伯遙子、十七歳です！」　……どうかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to be a dazzling presence‚ yeah… like the sun!\nI've thought of a new catchphrase‚ will you listen to it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんは二十歳の大学生ですよね？\n本当にそれでいいんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "'Haruko Saeki‚ 17 years old!' ……What do you think?\nHaruko-san‚ you're a 20 years old college student‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "い……いいわよ！　いいに決まってるじゃない！\n誰がなんと言おうと、私は若くて眩しい十七歳なのっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you sure that's okay?\nI-It's fine! Of course it'll be okay!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――さらに、またまた30分後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No matter what anyone says‚ I'm a young‚ dazzling 17 years old!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 196.1669433277,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "お茶が入ったわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――And then‚ another 30 minutes later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.2336092314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_05-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん、お茶淹れ過ぎです\nもうお茶でお腹一杯です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've made some tea\nHaruko-san‚ you made too much tea",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 203.4354195595,
